        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Reject Modal Structure -->
      <div id="reject" class="modal">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <h4>No problem, better swapping next time!</h4>
        <p>[ITEM NAME] will be returned back to your shop and [FRIEND'S NAME] will be notified! Be sure to check out [FRIEND'S NAME]'s shop to see if there is something else you would be willing to trade.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
